description: Expansion of Jacobi form of weight 12 and index 1 for the Niemeier lattice of type E_8^3 or D_16+E_8.
comments: a(4*n-r^2) gives number of vectors x in the lattice of norm 2n and <x,y>=r for any fixed vector in the lattice of norm 2.
references: M. Eichler and D. Zagier, The Theory of Jacobi Forms, Birkhauser, 1985.
author: Kok Seng Chua (chuaks(AT)ihpc.nus.edu.sg), Jul 11 2000
